{"tid":810993,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"比人誤會我搵援交","createTime":"2018-09-08T12:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T12:42:20.000Z","uid":70065,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6d973755065c7a9c916ebe81ad0b968c76b204ad","tid":810993,"uid":70065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:15:19.000Z","msg":"小弟有兩個女 大女今日上中五 本身家庭和睦<br />\n兩個女不嬲出街都時不時會拖下我<br />\n但平時都係一家人出街 人地見到我地一家四口 都會覺得我地感情好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁尋日開學日 我見都得閒 就諗住接個大女放學 順便買埋送返屋企 係接佢之前我都有短訊左大女<br />\n<br />\n問題黎喇 大女一見到係學校門口 就拖我隻手 話好多年都無接過佢放學 佢好開心 同時我見到學校其他人見到我地咁 我總係感覺佢地既眼神有d古怪 <br />\n我原本都以為係好少中學生比人接放學 都正常既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但今日大女放學返到屋企好唔開心 同我講 佢比人以為佢同個呀叔唔知做咩咁 比人唱 所以想我唔洗再接佢放學 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為父親 應如何自處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1112b2180317e0aab2e3b4d06d6fd87213296d32","tid":810993,"uid":113178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:16:34.000Z","msg":"Gay/10"},{"pid":"9e798ae5550adae0f548c75d20d24dd634b853df","tid":810993,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:17:56.000Z","msg":"難得中五仲同你咁close"},{"pid":"6e561bdb003873c58bc03d7a9d0de97fcd9143ec","tid":810993,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a5a0bfdaede5cb13cfa319ef60e99ab6d3e6a1","tid":810993,"uid":156520,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T12:21:54.000Z","msg":"上次俾你啲錢，夠唔夠用？"},{"pid":"149848efb3fd2c725077bcaef54ce182352a0e3a","tid":810993,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01a5a0bfdaede5cb13cfa319ef60e99ab6d3e6a1","tid":810993,"uid":156520,"like":9